data.description: POOL PARADISE IS POSSIBLE AT AN AFFORDABLE PRICE IN VENICE!  Can you imagine that you can live in a fully upgraded 2019 home over 2K square feet in Venice Florida just few miles to beach in a  3/3 WITH a den SALT WATER POOL HOME?!?  Now you can!  With over $150,000 in upgrades, this home truly stands out from the rest!  Your one-of-a-kind upgraded pool home in the highly sought-after location of the gated community of Watercrest is just a few miles from historic downtown Venice and the best Gulf beaches in South West Florida.  Low HOA no CDD!  Prepare to be amazed as you step into this totally upgraded 3 bed/3 bath with over 2,000,00 square feet of living space WITH ADDITIONAL office/flex room, boasting a designer pool and built in outdoor kitchen with granite.   Sheer opulence surrounds you, providing ample space for your indoor-outdoor Florida lifestyle. The split floor plan is easy and open, light and bright and move in ready to make new memories for you and your loved ones. Upgrades include but not limited to a custom, built in TV/electric Fireplace with Shiplap, Custom blinds on sliding doors, extra high ceilings, extra high triple sliders, designer chandelier and lighting and fans, custom shiplap entry wall, custom wainscoting, shelving and shiplap in laundry room, privacy shades on lanai, , Cambria quartz Ironsbridge accenting the face of the kitchen island, undermount extra-large stainless-steel sink, designer lighted pendants, custom tile backsplash and don’t forget the brand-new KitchenAid appliances with convection oven.   No carpeting here!  This treasure has fully upgraded plank flooring throughout the entire home and is kid-proof, pet-proof, and low-maintenance Everlife® LVP & LVT, offering on-trend wood looks without the worry. With industry-leading certifications and best-in-class ASTM testing performance, you can have peace of mind and enjoy your worry-free floors.   Entertain your friends and family in style with the lanai's exquisite outdoor dry bar, featuring custom soft-close doors, a refrigerator, and 100% weatherproof cabinetry with a granite countertop. Plus, the lanai is equipped with a heated saltwater pool with a sun shelf and bubblers, all enclosed in a screened-in cage for your privacy and comfort.  Don't worry about pool backyard privacy - the HOA new gated fence behind pool area will be installed by the time you move in!   The master bedroom exudes luxury with its custom walk-in closet with custom shelving installed and designer fan. The master en-suite bathroom is equally impressive, featuring two undermount sinks with soapstone quartz and a new vanity. The upgraded chrome faucets, frameless shower door, stunning penny tile flooring in the shower with dual shower heads adds a touch of elegance to your personal spa experience designed for the finest in relaxation splendor.  This maintenance-free home offers the perfect Florida lifestyle. Enjoy the cabana, resort heated zero-entry pool, and fitness center, all within the gated community.  Start enjoying your stunning pool Venice offers some of the most beautiful beaches, variety of restaurants , sensational shopping, best boating, fun shark tooth hunting, shelling, biking on  legacy trail and so much more!    You have to see it to believe it so watch the video >>>  https://vimeo.com/847760445  <<- and schedule your showing today!
